snippet.title: SMS Multiplayer - YouTube Trailer
snippet.description:
An in depth glimpse of what it’d be like if Super Mario Sunshine featured multiplayer. 

During this project, I ensured the quality of its concept, though I wasn’t able to assess 100% console compatibility and overall performance due to time constraints. This project was created and distributed by Founder of Blastsoft Studios, Michael Luaces. 

For copyright purposes, a download link will not be provided, as I do not condone piracy in any fashion. Please support the wonderful world of Nintendo by purchasing their products. 

Thanks for watching.
